source: TEXT_FESHLW2021ENTRANCE_00733_PIERROTFAMILYSERVANT00733_000_000<tab>I fear we're still making preparations for the feast. Pray wait a while longer!

TEXT_FESHLW2021ENTRANCE_00733_PIERROTFAMILYSERVANT00733_000_001<tab>I'm frightfully sorry for having kept you waiting. Do you wish to head to the banquet now? Master Gruff is eagerly anticipating your arrival.
target: TEXT_FESHLW2021ENTRANCE_00733_PIERROTFAMILYSERVANT00733_000_001<tab>Merrrci pour votre patience<var 1D /var>! Voulez-vous prendre part au banquet<var 1D /var>?
